## 0. Genre

Genre: Music

Explain why this genre fits your app idea: 
The app is inspired by The Midnight Gospel. Instead of exploring random planets, users travel through surreal music worlds that represent different emotions, genres, and vibes. Each world helps users discover new songs and organize playlists based on how they feel. 
## 1. Backstory
People often know what mood they’re in but don’t know what music to listen to. Instead of scrolling through endless playlists, this app lets users explore different “music worlds”, As they explore, they can discover songs and build playlists in a more fun and creative way. 

